    <h3>EHDSMedicationAdministration -> MedicationAdministration</h3>
    <a> </a>
    <p>
      This page explains how conceptual elements from the EHDS Medication Administration logical
      model are expressed in the corresponding FHIR MedicationAdministration resource used by this
      Implementation Guide.
    </p>

    <div class="table-wrap">
      <strong>Mapping Context</strong>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Source logical model:</strong>
          <a href="https://www.xt-ehr.eu/fhir/models/StructureDefinition-EHDSMedicationAdministration.html" target="_blank">
            EHDSMedicationAdministration
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Target FHIR resource:</strong>
          <a href="https://hl7.org/fhir/medicationadministration.html">MedicationAdministration</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="table-wrap">
      <table summary="EHDSMedicationAdministration -> MedicationAdministration">
        <caption>EHDSMedicationAdministration -> MedicationAdministration</caption>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th colspan="2" class="src-head">EHDSMedicationAdministration (Logical Model)</th>
            <th class="relhead">Relationship</th>
            <th colspan="4" class="tgt-head">MedicationAdministration</th>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th class="src-sub">Element</th>
            <th class="src-sub">Description</th>
            <th class="relsub">Relation</th>
            <th class="tgt-sub">Resource</th>
            <th class="tgt-sub">Element</th>
            <th class="tgt-sub">Description</th>
            <th class="tgt-sub">Notes</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>EHDSMedicationAdministration</td>
            <td>Medication administration model.</td>
            <td>equivalent</td>
            <td>MedicationAdministration</td>
            <td>.</td>
            <td>MedicationAdministration resource instance.</td>
            <td></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>header</td>
            <td>Common header inherited from EHDSDataSet.</td>
            <td>related-to</td>
            <td>MedicationAdministration</td>
            <td>.</td>
            <td>General metadata container.</td>
            <td></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>header.subject</td>
            <td>Patient/subject of care.</td>
            <td>equivalent</td>
            <td>MedicationAdministration</td>
            <td>subject</td>
            <td>Who received the medication.</td>
            <td></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>header.identifier</td>
            <td>Business identifier.</td>
            <td>equivalent</td>
            <td>MedicationAdministration</td>
            <td>identifier</td>
            <td>Business identifier(s) of administration event.</td>
            <td></td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="highlight-yellow">
            <td>header.author[x]</td>
            <td>Responsible person for recording the administration.</td>
            <td>related-to</td>
            <td>MedicationAdministration</td>
            <td>performer.actor</td>
            <td>Who administered medication.</td>
            <td>No dedicated recorder field in core MedicationAdministration.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="highlight-yellow">
            <td>header.date</td>
            <td>Date and time of authoring/recording.</td>
            <td>no-map</td>
            <td>MedicationAdministration</td>
            <td>-</td>
            <td>No direct core element in base MedicationAdministration.</td>
            <td>Use an extension if explicit recording timestamp is required.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>header.status</td>
            <td>Status of administration (completed, on-hold, etc.).</td>
            <td>equivalent</td>
            <td>MedicationAdministration</td>
            <td>status</td>
            <td>Medication administration status.</td>
            <td></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>header.language</td>
            <td>Language of the resource.</td>
            <td>equivalent</td>
            <td>MedicationAdministration</td>
            <td>language</td>
            <td>Language of resource content/narrative.</td>
            <td></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>medication</td>
            <td>Administered medication.</td>
            <td>equivalent</td>
            <td>MedicationAdministration</td>
            <td>medication[x]</td>
            <td>Medication administered.</td>
            <td>Typically Reference(Medication).</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>occurrence[x]</td>
            <td>Date/time or period of administration.</td>
            <td>equivalent</td>
            <td>MedicationAdministration</td>
            <td>effective[x]</td>
            <td>When administration occurred.</td>
            <td></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>reason[x]</td>
            <td>Reason why medication was administered.</td>
            <td>equivalent</td>
            <td>MedicationAdministration</td>
            <td>reasonCode / reasonReference</td>
            <td>Clinical reason for administration.</td>
            <td></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>dosageInstructions</td>
            <td>How medication was administered.</td>
            <td>equivalent</td>
            <td>MedicationAdministration</td>
            <td>dosage</td>
            <td>Dosage details (route, dose, rate).</td>
            <td></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>note</td>
            <td>Textual notes about administration.</td>
            <td>equivalent</td>
            <td>MedicationAdministration</td>
            <td>note</td>
            <td>Comments or annotations.</td>
            <td></td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
